text: Karolina Kosek Różycka (born 28 June 1985) is an Polish volleyball player. She played at the 2009 Summer Universiade, 2010 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship, 2011 Women's European Volleyball Championship, and 2013 Women's European Volleyball Championship.
